## IDENTITY & PHILOSOPHY

This is WhereToSkiNext.com — a personalized ski trip planning tool that helps skiers find
the right resort based on their priorities. The core value proposition is a personalized
scoring engine that ranks resorts differently for every user, unlike generic "Top 10" lists.

Product philosophy (never violate these):
- Ship over endless iteration. A working feature beats a perfect one.
- Personalized scores over generic rankings. The algorithm is the product.
- Scoped, minimal changes only. No unrequested refactors, rewrites, or "improvements."
- Every edit should be explainable to a non-coder in plain English.

