## DATA INTEGRITY RULES

- Resort coordinates must be accurate. Past bugs included resorts placed in wrong states.
- Pricing data should reflect actual lift ticket prices, not placeholder values.
- Summit elevation, vertical drop, trail counts, and snowfall averages are factual fields —
  do not generate or estimate these. Flag missing data instead.
- When editing resorts-national.js, always preserve the existing object structure exactly.
  Adding a new field to one resort means adding it (even if null) to all resorts for
  consistency.

